ration polo jeans company llc ralph lauren home collections inc ralph lauren media llc ralph lauren watch and jewelry company sàrl  rl fragrances llc website ralphlaurencom ralph lauren corporation nyse rl is an american corporation they are known for the clothing marketing and distribution of products in four categories apparel home accessories and fragrances the companys brands include polo ralph lauren ralph lauren collection lauren ralph lauren double rl ralph lauren childrenswear denim  supply ralph lauren chaps and club monaco ralph lauren corporation is an american publicly traded holding company headquartered in new york city and founded in  by american fashion designer ralph lauren contents  history  brands  stores  sports sponsorships  philanthropy  controversy  references  external links  see also historyedit polo ralph lauren – the flagship brand of the company the ralph lauren corporation started in  with mens ties at  yearsold lauren worked for the tie manufacturer beau brummell he persuaded the companys president to let him start his own line drawing on his interests in sports lauren named his first full line of menswear ‘polo’ in  he worked out of a single drawer from a showroom in the empire state building and made deliveries to stores himself by  the manhattan department store bloomingdales sold laurens men line exclusively it was the first time that bloomingdales had given a designer his own instore shop in  ralph lauren corporation launched a line of tailored shirts for women which introduced the polo player emblem appearing on the shirt cuff the first full womens collection was launched the following year  also marked the opening of ralph laurens store on rodeo drive in beverly hills california his first freestanding storecitation needed in  ralph lauren corporation introduced a signature cotton mesh polo shirt in various colours featuring the polo player logo on the chest the shirt became emblematic of the preppy look—one of laurens signature stylecitation needed in  ralph lauren outfitted the male cast of the great gatsby in costumes chosen from his polo line  a sstyle series of mens suits and sweaters except for the pink suit which lauren designed especially for robert redford’s jay gatsby in  diane keaton and woody allen wore laurens clothes in the oscarwinning film annie hall in  the first ralph lauren fragrances produced by warnerlauren ltd were launched at bloomingdales lauren for women and polo the mens cologne this was the first time that a designer introduced two fragrances – one for men and one for women – simultaneouslycitation needed the company entered the european market and went international in  with the opening of the first freestanding store in new bond street in the west end of london england lauren opened his first flagship in the rhinelander mansion on madison avenue and nd street in new york city in  on june   the company becomes a publicly traded company on the new york stock exchange the seat restaurant rl opened in march  in a newlyconstructed building adjacent to the largest ralph lauren store at the corner of chicago and michigan avenues it was followed by the opening of two additional restaurants – ralphs at  boulevard saint germain paris store in  and the polo bar at polos store in new york in  the company launched its website and online shop in  as polocom by rl media a cooperation between ralph lauren and nbc in  ralph lauren corporation acquired the nbc share of rl media and the website was relaunched as ralphlaurencom in september  it was announced that stefan larsson would replace the companys founder ralph lauren as ceo in november lauren will stay on as executive chairman and chief creative officer in february  it was announced that larsson had agreed to leave his position as ceo effective may   due to differences with lauren on may   ralph lauren named patrice louvet president and chief executive officer louvet most recently served as group president global beauty at procter  gamble pg he will take over on july   brandsedit a wool polo ralph lauren scarf ralph lauren womens collection and ralph lauren purple label ralph lauren collection for women launched in  ranges from handmade evening gowns to sportswear launched in  ralph lauren purple label for men offers suiting custom tailored madetomeasure suits and sportswear as well as benchmade footwear and madetoorder dress furnishings accessories and luggage ralph lauren watches and fine jewelry in  ralph lauren together with luxury group compagnie financière richemont sa launched a collection of timepieces through the ralph lauren watch  jewelry co in  the ralph lauren watch  jewelry co also introduced collections of jewelry polo ralph lauren men’s polo ralph lauren’s first complete line of sportswear and tailored clothing launched in  in  women’s polo was launched polo sport polo sport launched in  a line of activewear for sports and fitness in  ralph lauren debuted the polotech shirt which featured smart fabric technology that supposedly captures robust biometrics from the wearer double rl founded in  and named after ralph lauren and his wife rickys “rrl” ranch in colorado rrl offers men a mix of selvage denim vintage apparel sportswear and accessories with roots in workwear and military gear lauren ralph lauren lauren for women launched in  offering sportswear denim dresses activewear and accessories and footwear at a cheaper price point lauren for men offers mens tailored clothing including suits sport coats dress shirts dress pants tuxedos topcoats and ties at a cheaper price point ralph by ralph lauren launched in  ralph by ralph lauren offers suit separates sport coats vests and topcoats polo golf and rlx golf polo golf launched in  and rlx golf launched in  pink pony established in  a percentage of sales from all pink pony products benefit the pink pony fund and other major cancer charities around the world pink pony primarily consists of womens sportswear and accessories a